Class Sessions

  • java.lang.Object

    Serializable, Comparable<Sessions>

    public class Sessions
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<Sessions>
    English:
    contains the session information. Used to load the open sessions. Some dead sessions can be closed at the client side.
